title: Limit of nonlinear Signorini problems for incompressible materials
authors: Edoardo Mainini, Danilo Percivale, Robertus van der Putten
abstract:
The paper is devoted to the linearization of the non linear Signorini
functional in the incompressible case. The limit functional, in the sense of
Gamma-convergence, may coincide with the expected one only in some particular
cases.
